> Sunhawk:  Hey general Talos I caught some Preds digging for energon
> and this one was put in stasis lock by an energon wave.  I'm not
> sure, but I suspect the other's were as well.  I request permission
> to lock up the prisoner and take some troops to get the other's that
> were there.
>

{Talos}

    Talos nodded looking down at Sunhawks captive, apparently caught in the
throes of stasis lock more so than battle damage. "Take her to the brig then
round up Grimlock, Kup and Condor to help you." Turning from the bot he
opened a comm channel, "Kenzo, report to the brig, Sunhawk is delivering a
prisoner down there and I'd like you to make sure she's all right, I want
her functional for when I question her."
